    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "it just seems like a lot of hassle for something so small. i'm not really feeling sick or anything, just the site is a bit irritated. if i just use a bit of hydrogen peroxide to clean it and then put on a hydrocortisone cream to bring the redness down, wouldn't that help? it's just a tiny little bump, i don't think i'm actually infected.",
